'''''Yeelen''''' ( Bambara kuri "umucyo" / "urumuri") ni film yo muri [[Mali]] yakinwe muri 1987 iyobowe na Souleymane Cissé<ref>Film Notes -Yeelen - University at Albany <nowiki>https://www.albany.edu</nowiki> › writers-inst › webpages4 › fil...</ref> . Ifata amashusho mu ndimi za Bambara na Fula, kandi ishingiye ku mugani wabwiwe n'abaturage ba Bambara<ref>More than a Malian Monomyth: Close-Up on “Yeelen” - MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › notebook › posts › more-than-a-mal...</ref> . Nubwo ibihe bitarasobanurwa neza, birashoboka ko byashyizweho mu kinyejana cya 13 mu bwami bwa Mali <ref>[https://www.criterionchannel.com/yeelen The Criterion Channel]</ref> kandi ni inkuru yo gushakisha ubutwari irimo ubumaji no kuvumbura. <ref>[https://www.albany.edu/writers-inst/webpages4/filmnotes/fns05n4.html Film Notes - Yeelen]</ref>

Irimo Issiaka Kane nka Nianankoro, umusore [[Afurika|wumunyafurika]] ufite imbaraga zubumaji<ref>Yeelen – trigon-film.org <nowiki>https://www.trigon-film.org</nowiki> › movies › Yeelen</ref>. Niamanto Sanogo akina nka se wa Niankoro, ukurikirana umuhungu we binyuze mu bihugu bya Bambara, Fulani na Dogon byo muri Afurika y'Iburengerazuba akoresheje inkingi y'ibiti by'amayobera kugira ngo amuyobore. <ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K0PmgaRmURI Yeelen - Brows Held High - KyleKallgrenBHH on YouTube]</ref>

