Yatowe muri Filime Nziza Mpuzamahanga muri Film Independent Spirit Awards . [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oKz68TZ9U4I Umuhango ngarukamwaka wa 4 wo gutanga ibihembo byumwuka wakiriwe na Buck Henry - igitaramo cyuzuye (1989) | Filime Yigenga kuri YouTube]

